	is NULL.
	(cyg_flash_init): No longer takes printf arg.
	(cyg_flash_set_printf): New. Set per-device printf function, locking
	if needed.
	(cyg_flash_set_global_printf): New. Set printf function for all
	devices, locking if needed.
	
